Easy fitment to front & rear wheel arches, using Black Japanned Philips pan head self-tapper screws provided. Screws keep the mudflap tighter against your car, preventing soil accumulating. This is the prefered method of fitment for most dealers. What's Included?: - Set (4) of blank mudflaps - Pack of 12 screws
